Class LString

java.lang.Object
  skeletonlisp.LExp.LExp
      skeletonlisp.LExp.LValue
          skeletonlisp.LExp.LString

public class LString
extends LValue

The LString class is the data-structural representation of SkeletonLisp's strings.

However only the interpreter uses strings.
